WEBVTT

00:00:00.840 --> 00:00:02.793
All right, I want to see a show of hands:

00:00:02.817 --> 00:00:05.216
how many of you have
unfriended someone on Facebook

00:00:05.240 --> 00:00:09.096
because they said something offensive
about politics or religion,

00:00:09.120 --> 00:00:11.256
childcare, food?

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:13.216
(Laughter)

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:16.056
And how many of you
know at least one person that you avoid

00:00:16.079 --> 00:00:18.360
because you just don't want
to talk to them?

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.936
(Laughter)

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:24.176
You know, it used to be that in order
to have a polite conversation,

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:27.416
we just had to follow the advice
of Henry Higgins in "My Fair Lady":

00:00:27.440 --> 00:00:29.256
Stick to the weather and your health.

00:00:29.280 --> 00:00:32.656
But these days, with climate change
and anti-vaxxing, those subjects --